redicted by scaling a\ntypical FSRQ jet by black hole mass and accretion rate. That gamma-ray emitting\nNLS1s appear to host underpowered jets may go some way to explaining why so few\nhave been detected to date.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 18:26:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
