ty dependence on grain radius $a$ may vary significantly\nbetween comets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 18:36:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Jan 2018 18:17:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-31"}
