) probability, indicating that we are\nprobing well within the reionization epoch of the Universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 19:00:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2018 17:30:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-09"}
