dB SNR gain at $10^{-4}$ bit error rate in $256$-QAM $16\\!\\times\\!16$ MIMO,\nwhile saving $77\\%$ of nulling-and-cancellation computations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 19:27:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-07"}
