t\nIVR is so slow that the molecule begins to dissociate well before such\nquasi-thermalization is complete, in accordance with earlier\nclassical-mechanical predictions of non-RRKM behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 20:30:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 17 Feb 2018 17:37:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-08"}
