wahori-Hecke category. We\ndeduce both the Ng\\^o action and its quantization from the case of the\nLanglands dual equivariant affine Grassmannian using the renormalized Geometric\nSatake theorem of Bezrukavnikov-Finkelberg.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Dec 2017 23:09:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-07"}
