 decisions to inputs. Moreover, DL can also use data to condition\nneurons that mimic problem-specific fundamental organizing units, thus\nrevealing emergent behaviors of these units. Vast opportunities exist for DL to\npropel advances in water sciences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Dec 2017 12:44:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2017 14:15:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2018 15:12:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
